<figureCitation id="DA72F767E9A2477E6C0C90062D683DD3" captionStart="Figure 38" captionStartId="F38" captionText="Figure 38. Aloe saundersiae. Photo: N. R. Crouch." figureDoi="10.3897/phytokeys.142.48365.figure38" httpUri="https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/388264" pageId="0" pageNumber="1">38</figureCitation>
).
</paragraph>
